		{"id":"grp_conn","type":"group","x":-60,"y":-120,"width":420,"height":500,"color":"4","label":"① Connection / Robot site (WebRTC single peer)"},
		{"id":"grp_viz","type":"group","x":420,"y":-500,"width":860,"height":130,"color":"1","label":"⑥ Visualization"},
		{"id":"cut2_box","type":"group","x":428,"y":-74,"width":324,"height":128,"color":"#f08c00","label":"cut②"},
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# unitree-go2-agentic-local-tts — module pipeline\n\nSTT = local JA Whisper · LLM = swappable OpenAI-compat (`DIMOS_LLM_MODEL/BASE_URL/API_KEY`) · **TTS = local Style-Bert-VITS2 (JA)**\nComposition: `unitree_go2_basic` → `unitree_go2` → `unitree_go2_spatial_bounded` → `_common_agentic_ja` + `McpServer` + `TimedMcpClient`  (`SecurityModule` disabled)","x":420,"y":-700,"width":860,"height":140,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"vis","type":"text","text":"**vis_module**\nRerun 3D + camera view · WebsocketVis command center → http://localhost:7779","x":440,"y":-470,"width":820,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"go2","type":"text","text":"🐕 **Unitree Go2** (hardware)\nonboard MCU: gait control 500Hz–1kHz + obstacle avoidance\n→ stays local, never crosses the network","x":-20,"y":-60,"width":300,"height":90,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"conn","type":"text","text":"**GO2Connection**  (WebRTC peer — single)\nout: color_image ~14Hz · lidar ~10Hz (→world) · odom ~50Hz\nin: cmd_vel (Twist) / sport command\nclose Unitree phone app first (single-peer)","x":-20,"y":120,"width":320,"height":170,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"voxel","type":"text","text":"**VoxelGridMapper** [CUDA]\nlidar点群を5cmボクセルに蓄積。column carving =\n同(X,Y)列の旧ボクセルを消去→常に最新形状\n`emit_every=5` → global_map (PointCloud2) ~7.8Hz","x":440,"y":-60,"width":300,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"cost","type":"text","text":"**CostMapper**\nglobal_map → `height_cost` で 3D点群→2D\n→ global_costmap (OccupancyGrid) ~7.6Hz","x":440,"y":100,"width":300,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"astar","type":"text","text":"**ReplanningAStarPlanner**\nin: global_costmap + odom + goal\nGlobalPlanner が A* で連続リプランニング\nout: path (viz) / nav_cmd_vel (Twist)","x":440,"y":240,"width":300,"height":110,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"move","type":"text","text":"**MovementManager**\nnav_cmd_vel と tele_cmd_vel を mux\n(手動優先・cooldown 1s, ナビ goal は cancel)\nout: cmd_vel (Twist)","x":440,"y":410,"width":300,"height":90,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"frontier","type":"text","text":"**WavefrontFrontierExplorer**\nin: global_costmap + odom + goal_reached\n既知/未知の境界(frontier)を選択\nout: goal_request (PoseStamped)","x":440,"y":560,"width":300,"height":90,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"perceive","type":"text","text":"**PerceiveLoopSkill**\nperception loop over camera","x":880,"y":-60,"width":300,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"spatial","type":"text","text":"**SpatialMemoryBounded**\nbounded spatial memory (objects + positions)","x":880,"y":90,"width":300,"height":90,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"sec","type":"text","text":"**SecurityModule**\npresent via spatial_bounded but\n`.disabled_modules(SecurityModule)` → OFF here","x":880,"y":250,"width":300,"height":90},
		{"id":"navskill","type":"text","text":"**NavigationSkillContainer**\nnav goal skills","x":1340,"y":-180,"width":300,"height":70,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"followskill","type":"text","text":"**PersonFollowSkillContainer**","x":1340,"y":-80,"width":300,"height":70,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"unitreeskill","type":"text","text":"**UnitreeSkillContainer**\nsport cmds (pose / jump / stand)","x":1340,"y":20,"width":300,"height":70,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"mcpserver","type":"text","text":"**McpServer**\nexposes skill containers as MCP tools","x":1340,"y":130,"width":300,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"agent","type":"text","text":"**TimedMcpClient**  (LLM Agent)\nJA system prompt\nendpoint via DIMOS_LLM_MODEL / BASE_URL / API_KEY\n(OpenAI cloud · Azure · local vLLM/Ollama on DGX Spark)\nsubscribes spatial context · calls MCP tools · emits text","x":1340,"y":280,"width":340,"height":170,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"ptt","type":"text","text":"**PttKeyboard**  (F9 push-to-talk)","x":1800,"y":-180,"width":300,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"mic","type":"text","text":"**LocalMicrophoneJa**\nPTT-gated utterance recorder","x":1800,"y":-80,"width":300,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"stt","type":"text","text":"**WhisperHumanInputJa**  (STT)\nlocal JA-tuned Whisper → /human_input","x":1800,"y":80,"width":300,"height":90,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"tts","type":"text","text":"**AssistantSpeechNodeJa**  (TTS)\nStyle-Bert-VITS2 (local, JA) → 🔊 speaker","x":1800,"y":260,"width":300,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"cut1_line","type":"text","text":"","x":386,"y":-545,"width":8,"height":1340,"color":"#e03131"},
		{"id":"cut3_line","type":"text","text":"","x":846,"y":-545,"width":8,"height":1340,"color":"#9c36b5"},
		{"id":"cut4_line","type":"text","text":"","x":1286,"y":-545,"width":8,"height":1340,"color":"#1971c2"},
		{"id":"legend","type":"text","text":"## APN cut overlay\n\n縦線 = APN 境界の候補（**左 = ロボット拠点 / 右 = 遠隔拠点**）。\n線を横切るエッジ = その cut で **APN を渡るトラフィック**。\n\n色: 🔴cut① / 🟠cut② / 🟣cut③ / 🔵cut④\n上流ほど薄いエッジ（APN依存大・showcase強）、下流ほど堅牢。","x":-460,"y":-700,"width":420,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"cut1_h","type":"text","text":"### 🔴 cut① — thin edge / raw relay  ★推奨\n**Robot site:** GO2Connection のみ（**GPU不要**）\n**APN payload:** raw lidar+video+odom ↓ / cmd_vel ↑\n**閉ループが APN を横断** → APN 低遅延が最も効く・A/B 差最大\nリスク: 帯域と遅延に最も厳しい。decoupling 物語は完璧。","x":-460,"y":-470,"width":420,"height":210,"color":"#e03131"},
		{"id":"cut2_h","type":"text","text":"### 🟠 cut② — after mapping\n= cut① + **VoxelGridMapper を robot 側に残す**（**要GPU@robot**）\n**APN payload:** voxel/global map ↓ / goal ↑\n中間案。decoupling 物語は半分（頭脳の一部が現地）。","x":-460,"y":-230,"width":420,"height":170,"color":"#f08c00"},
		{"id":"cut3_h","type":"text","text":"### 🟣 cut③ — nav loop 全体ローカル\n**Robot site:** Connection + 全 Mapping/Nav（**要GPU@robot**）\n**APN payload:** costmap+video+pose / 高レベル目標\n閉ループはローカル → **APN 低遅延ほぼ不要**（A/B 差小）。","x":-460,"y":-30,"width":420,"height":180,"color":"#9c36b5"},
		{"id":"cut4_h","type":"text","text":"### 🔵 cut④ — agent 境界  ☂フォールバック\n**Robot site:** Connection + Nav + Perception（要GPU@robot）\n**Remote:** LLM Agent + Voice I/O のみ\n**APN payload:** video+pose ↓ / 目標(text) ↑\n最も堅牢。LLM TTFT 500ms が律速 → **APN 優位ほぼ無**。","x":-460,"y":180,"width":420,"height":200,"color":"#1971c2"},
		{"id":"patrol","type":"text","text":"**PatrollingModule**\nin: global_costmap + odom + goal_reached\ncoverage router で巡回点を選択\nout: goal_request (PoseStamped)","x":440,"y":680,"width":300,"height":90,"color":"2"}
	],
